a:5:{s:5:"title";s:41:"Day.ai tables now remember your last view";s:16:"text-format-info";a:3:{s:10:"text-final";s:430:"<p>When navigating away from a table and returning, Day.ai restores the last viewed saved view instead of resetting to the default, reducing repeated re-filtering.</p>
